insta , pinterest , mozilla , spotify backend , disqus comments , this all apps use django -style architectures coz its fast scalable and secure

Django miku emi help chestundi?
1Ô∏è‚É£Fast development
.Code chala thakkuva
.Features chala ekkuva
.Development speed super

2Ô∏è‚É£ Security
.Django automatically protects:
.SQL Injection
.Cross-site scripting
