.. why do we create a project in django
coz a prj is d main foundation of ur entire website .
think of it like this :
a django project = full website skeleton 
a django app = one feature inside that website

without d proj , django doest know 
which apps u created 
which db to use 
which urls exist 
how tekplates should load
how d whole site should run 

so proj  is mandatory its at d top level

Simple Real-Life Example

Let‚Äôs say you're building an app like BookMyShow.

Your project name: bookmyshow

Inside this project, you might create apps:

users (login, signup)

movies (movie list)

booking (tickets)

payment (payment gateway)

notifications (emails / SMS)

All these apps must live inside one project.
_______+++++++++++_________________
If you don't create a project ‚Üí
apps ki home (environment) undadu ‚Üí site run avadu.
_________________-------------___________________


in project we have some files those are :- asgi.py , settings.py , urls.py , manage.py , wsgi.py ok

manage.py :- u use it to run almost all django commands

run server :- python manage.py runserver
. create apps
command :- python manage.py startapp app_name (siva)
and then do migrations 
commands :- python msnsge.py makemigrations
inko command vachi python.manage.py migrate 

..// settings.py
this is the heart of d project 
everything imp is stored here:
installed apps , database settings , templates settings , staic files middleware , secret key , debug key , allowed hosts without settings.py project will not run

..// urls.py :- this is the route manager.
it decides which url should go to which view ?

..// wsgi.py :- used when deploying ur django proj on a server (apache,nginx , etc.)

django app run avvadani ki server ki needed file

// asgi.py :- used for asynchronous applications
fastAPi style features :
.websockets
.chat apps 
.realtime notifications
File	             Use	                          Meaning
manage.py	       commands	                         Main control
init.py	           Makes folder a package	         Technical setup
settings.py	      All project settings	                Heart
urls.py	            URL routing                        	Map
wsgi.py	         Deploy on server	                  Production gateway
asgi.py	          Async support	                      Realtime gateway

